item.title: 【HD Live Performances】REQUEST - AIR MOON SAFARI livestream from London Royal Albert Hall
item.description:
AIR GLOBAL LIVESTREAM FROM LONDON’S ROYAL ALBERT HALL TONIGHT!
IN PARTNERSHIP WITH DRIIFT & LA BLOGOTHÈQUE

AIR have resumed their MOON SAFARI tour in Europe at London’s iconic Royal Albert Hall after a short detour at the Sydney Opera Hall

The London shows are sold out but there’s still a chance to see the band perform at this very special venue as tonight’s show will be livestreamed around the world.

Livestream: Friday 31 May 9pm London-time (BST)
Rebroadcast #1: Friday 31 May 9pm New York-time (EDT)
Rebroadcast #2: Friday 31 May 9pm Los Angeles-time (PDT)
On Demand: Saturday 1 June 7am (BST) - Tuesday 4 June 7am (BST)

I have my livestream ticket! But I don't have capability to capture this... If anyone does, please post it! THANK YOU!
